{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then one part of our people was doing that, some other-- the other part was building the barracks for where to stay.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Warsaw was not so bad-- not as bad as Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that-- and-- and my job in Warsaw was, they call him the spring commando.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The spring commando is to bomb down the-- when the bomb-- the Germans, they fought with the Jews in Warsaw, it was part of the houses was standing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's one in one wall, some in two walls, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some was falling down by themselves, because there was very much from the bombs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they put us over there to-- to make a hole in the wall and put the sticks of dynamites inside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans themselves were afraid, because the wall may fall down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they send ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somebody-- the wall fell down, it's no big deal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another Jew die-- no big deal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So some of them-- people I knew there-- you know, you go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You put the stick in, and you run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the guy puts the thing on, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some-- sometimes, I was very close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes the-- the building almost fall on top of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes it missed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we did that till we clean up the whole-- everything that-- the whole-- the whole Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We make it flat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a fight between the Germans and the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I find out later, much later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so-- and after they build the thing, the Germans, they want the bricks to take it to Germany in their-- in their thing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we did is we have to clean up the bricks and pile 'em up to 250 each.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
